storyInfo: Ho'olheyak shows up at the bar to stop the former scientist from revealing too much. The Doctor and the Rhodes Islanders give chase, but find themselves once again waylaid by power armor. Back at the test site, Silence and Elena dig into the experiment data and find its goals increasingly suspicious.

attributes.content: We don't know you.
attributes.name: Saria

attributes.content: Really?
attributes.name: Ho

attributes.content: How sad.
attributes.name: Ho

attributes.content: One Siestan Iced Tea, please.
attributes.name: Ho

attributes.content: For this gentleman.
attributes.name: Ho

attributes.content: Burp...
attributes.name: Drunkard

attributes.content: What's the matter?
attributes.name: Saria

attributes.content: He's shivering. Must be the air conditioning in the bar.
attributes.name: Ho

attributes.content: Have another drink, it'll warm you up.
attributes.name: Ho

attributes.content: Er, no...
attributes.name: Drunkard

attributes.content: Oh, I forgot. Your tastes have changed.
attributes.name: Ho

attributes.content: Your favorite drink was Siestan Iced Tea, back when you could still hold a scalpel. Strong enough to make you forget Loken Williams's abuse.
attributes.name: Ho

attributes.content: Now, he has a hundred and twenty-two years left on his prison term, while you... you're free.
attributes.name: Ho

attributes.content: Free... you're talking to me about free?
attributes.name: Drunkard

attributes.content: I've been uploading my biometric data on a monthly basis, just like you told me...
attributes.name: Drunkard

attributes.content: Shh.
attributes.name: Ho

attributes.content: Let's not talk about work here.
attributes.name: Ho

attributes.content: We come to the bar to relax, don't we?
attributes.name: Ho

attributes.content: Or would you rather drink with these two? One whose face shows no expression, the other whose face can't be seen at all... than with your old friend?
attributes.name: Ho

attributes.content: Old friend? Hah, that's rich.
attributes.name: Drunkard

attributes.content: The reason I've become this, it's all because...
attributes.name: Drunkard

attributes.content: Here's to freedom.
attributes.name: Ho

attributes.content: They left me no choice, Saria.
attributes.name: Drunkard

attributes.content: You're on your own.
attributes.name: Drunkard

attributes.content: The man picks up the glass and gulps down its contents.
He stares into space with a particular expression. It is hard to say whether it's one of anger, or one of despair.
A moment later, he falls from his chair.
His legs spasm as though shocked by electricity, while his left hand grasps at his right arm.
His fingers dig deep into his own flesh, as though trying to rip out the electronics that have caused him so much grief, along with his past sins.
Oh my god. What happened to him?
attributes.name: Bar Patron

attributes.content: Call an ambulance!
attributes.name: Bar Patron

attributes.options: Is he sick?;Something in the drink?

attributes.content: Epilepsy.
attributes.name: Saria

attributes.content: Blood test shows abnormal chemical composition.
attributes.name: Saria

attributes.content: That injection I gave him will help. He'll live.
attributes.name: Saria

attributes.content: That drink...
attributes.name: Saria

attributes.content: There's half a glass left... I'm not the type to waste.
attributes.name: Ho

attributes.content: You drank the rest?
attributes.name: Saria

attributes.content: As you just saw.
attributes.name: Ho

attributes.content: Still don't get it? Check out your friend's teeth.
attributes.name: Ho

attributes.content: Second molar on the left.
attributes.name: Ho

attributes.content: A false tooth.
attributes.name: Saria

attributes.content: He did one final operation on himself before he left Loken Watertank.
attributes.name: Ho

attributes.content: You knew it all along.
attributes.name: Saria

attributes.content: I should have removed the variable myself. One tooth wouldn't have affected his work.
attributes.name: Ho

attributes.content: But I didn't.
attributes.name: Ho

attributes.content: I believe we in Columbia should have the freedom to embrace death.
attributes.name: Ho

attributes.content: Doctor—
attributes.name: Saria

attributes.content: Take the patient, and give us some space.
attributes.name: Saria

attributes.content: We have a problem and we need to deal with it.
attributes.name: Saria

attributes.content: Sir, the new test results are out!
attributes.name: Rhine Lab Tech

attributes.content: Let's hope it justifies this commotion.
attributes.name: Ferdinand

attributes.content: Sixty-seven percent?
attributes.name: Ferdinand

attributes.content: W-We tried our best.
attributes.name: Rhine Lab Tech

attributes.content: What about the retests?
attributes.name: Ferdinand

attributes.content: H-Here they are.
attributes.name: Rhine Lab Tech

attributes.content: Get me all the numbers.
attributes.name: Ferdinand

attributes.content: Yes... sir.
attributes.name: Rhine Lab Tech

attributes.content: Sir...
attributes.name: Rhine Lab Tech

attributes.content: I'll be damned, the old goat wasn't playing.
attributes.name: Ferdinand

attributes.content: It's all up to Ho'olheyak now... she'd better take care of Saria.
attributes.name: Ferdinand

attributes.content: I'm honored that the former head of Rhine's Defense Section thinks I'm a problem.
attributes.name: Ho

attributes.content: Who are you?
attributes.name: Saria

attributes.content: We've never met, Director Saria.
attributes.name: Ho

attributes.content: But I've heard of you.
attributes.name: Ho

attributes.content: One of the co-founders of Rhine Lab, graduate of the Trimounts Institute of Technology, who left academia after earning her PhD in biomedical engineering to become the head of the Defense Section.
attributes.name: Ho

attributes.content: Everyone associates Rhine Lab with Kirsten Wright, but few have heard of you.
attributes.name: Ho

attributes.content: Have you never resented that, after all these years?
attributes.name: Ho

attributes.content: That's unnecessary.
attributes.name: Saria

attributes.content: I made my choice, I took up my duty.
attributes.name: Saria

attributes.content: I know.
attributes.name: Ho

attributes.content: You think yourself a firefighter, but what you really love is the feeling of charging into a fire, am I right?
attributes.name: Ho

attributes.content: You like fighting.
attributes.name: Ho

attributes.content: That doesn't mean you're a warrior. You have no thirst for challenge and destruction.
attributes.name: Ho

attributes.content: That's why you never fit in with the scientific community.
attributes.name: Ho

attributes.content: Five years ago, you received a grafted plant from Muelsyse, who taught the vines to dance.
attributes.name: Ho

attributes.content: You accepted the gift. Thereafter, you were in your office by seven every morning, trimming the sprouts that had grown overeager.
attributes.name: Ho

attributes.content: You've been spying on Rhine Lab?
attributes.name: Saria

attributes.content: Maybe I just heard some office gossip.
attributes.name: Ho

attributes.content: Then maybe you missed the part where Muelsyse turned the offices of three directors into Sargon rainforests.
attributes.name: Saria

attributes.content: Or how much trouble it caused Defense.
attributes.name: Saria

attributes.content: Well then...
attributes.name: Ho

attributes.content: How much trouble did the Diαbolic business cause you?
attributes.name: Ho

attributes.content: For all the garbage you've talked, there's one thing you got right.
attributes.name: Saria

attributes.content: Hm?
attributes.name: Ho

attributes.content: I don't shy away from a fight.
attributes.name: Saria

attributes.content: Beautiful Arts.
attributes.name: Ho

attributes.content: Did you use that trick against Control?
attributes.name: Ho

attributes.content: You're too curious for a mercenary.
attributes.name: Saria

attributes.content: Hey, they're fighting!
attributes.name: Bar Patron

attributes.content: Are they drunk? Where's a bouncer when you need one?
attributes.name: Bar Patron

attributes.content: Are you the bouncer? Get them out of here!
attributes.name: Bar Patron

attributes.content: Sorry, I'm just a mechanist.
attributes.name: Mechanist

attributes.content: Hitting the road would be the smart choice here.
attributes.name: Mechanist

attributes.content: Shit! The ceiling's coming down! Go! Go!
attributes.name: Bar Patron

attributes.content: Are you okay, Doctor?
attributes.name: Mechanist

attributes.content: So eager to stop the fight...
attributes.name: Ho

attributes.content: Won't you stay a while longer?
attributes.name: Ho

attributes.content: There aren't many in Columbia who could take a hit from you and stay standing.
attributes.name: Ho

attributes.content: With skills like yours, there aren't many who could afford your fee.
attributes.name: Saria

attributes.content: This doesn't have much to do with Volvort Kochinski. And your style isn't military.
attributes.name: Saria

attributes.content: You're eager to kill the trail of the silver reagent.
attributes.name: Saria

attributes.content: Your employer could be Ferdinand, or it could be...
attributes.name: Saria

attributes.content: ...Control?
attributes.name: Ho

attributes.content: Even now, you still won't turn your suspicions towards her?
attributes.name: Ho

attributes.content: Too many questions to let you go.
attributes.name: Saria

attributes.content: Saria!
attributes.name: Mechanist

attributes.content: Saria takes note of her position and that of her colleague. The enemy's path of retreat is cut off.
There is no need to drag this out. She unleashes her Arts without hesitation.
An enamel wall appears out of thin air, and Saria takes aim at Ho'olheyak's vitals.
Looks like the time for talk is over.
attributes.name: Ho

attributes.content: You're not dodging?
attributes.name: Saria

attributes.content: Don't need to. I'm not in the habit of taking long shots.
attributes.name: Ho

attributes.content: Saria's fingers should have found her opponent's abdomen.
But she does not feel the warm touch of soft flesh.
There is no sign of pain on Ho'olheyak's face.
She leans forward, her lips nearly touching Saria's ear.
Believe it or not, Saria, I just wanted to chat.
attributes.name: Ho

attributes.content: I'm curious about you... about Rhine Lab.
attributes.name: Ho

attributes.content: You hurt my friend the moment you showed up. Doesn't exactly put me in a chatting mode.
attributes.name: Saria

attributes.content: Hehe... I have a job to do, after all.
attributes.name: Ho

attributes.content: One last parting word for you.
attributes.name: Ho

attributes.content: Don't be too eager to make an enemy of me.
attributes.name: Ho

attributes.content: Don't be too eager to make an enemy of anyone.
attributes.name: Ho

attributes.content: She got away? Why... is there a hole in the wall?
attributes.name: Mechanist

attributes.content: That was me.
attributes.name: Saria

attributes.content: Did her Arts misdirect you?
attributes.name: Mechanist

attributes.content: It was some technique, but not Originium Arts.
attributes.name: Saria

attributes.content: She changed the air composition around her, interfering with my Arts, and causing my attack to miss its target.
attributes.name: Saria

attributes.content: I've never seen anything like it before.
attributes.name: Saria

attributes.options: Muelsyse...;Could she keep a caster from getting at water molecules?

attributes.content: Muelsyse's disappearance may be her work too.
attributes.name: Mechanist

attributes.content: Maybe.
attributes.name: Mechanist

attributes.content: I've thought about it. Heating air in a specific direction is pretty mundane. It wouldn't have been enough to disable Muelsyse.
attributes.name: Mechanist

attributes.content: Doctor, I propose we go after her.
attributes.name: Saria

attributes.content: Whether it's the intel she has access to, or the strange techniques she uses...
attributes.name: Saria

attributes.content: This Liberi is extremely dangerous.
attributes.name: Saria

attributes.content: Officer? Where are you going?
attributes.name: Rhine Defense Section Employee

attributes.content: I didn't know I had to report my every move to you.
attributes.name: Mary

attributes.content: Records show you took the key to a vehicle...
attributes.name: Rhine Defense Section Employee

attributes.content: Just borrowing an asset.
attributes.name: Mary

attributes.content: By all means, report it to your miserable director.
attributes.name: Mary

attributes.content: Officer...
attributes.name: Rhine Defense Section Employee

attributes.content: What is it? I don't have all day.
attributes.name: Mary

attributes.content: Mary Banner. You grew up in the town of Steelham, north of Trimounts. Sonny Romano was your neighbor and middle school classmate.
attributes.name: Rhine Defense Section Employee

attributes.content: You've been investigating me?
attributes.name: Mary

attributes.content: Romano was registered as Infected four years ago. He ended his internship at a law firm and returned to Steelham. His insurance payments stopped six months later.
attributes.name: Rhine Defense Section Employee

attributes.content: His name resurfaced on the crew manifest for this Pioneer Team, three years and seventeen days later.
attributes.name: Rhine Defense Section Employee

attributes.content: Where was he during that time?
attributes.name: Rhine Defense Section Employee

attributes.content: How would I know?
attributes.name: Mary

attributes.content: Preventing problems before they occur is part of our job.
attributes.name: Rhine Defense Section Employee

attributes.content: If you thought you could scare me by raffling off some old records, think again.
attributes.name: Mary

attributes.content: It took me five years to get to where I am now. Did you think I don't know how to deal with some corporate worms?
attributes.name: Mary

attributes.content: Ahem. I have never doubted your ability.
attributes.name: Rhine Defense Section Employee

attributes.content: Then don't make me feed you to the tuskbeasts.
attributes.name: Mary

attributes.content: Maybe you don't believe it, but I just wanted to give you some friendly advice.
attributes.name: Rhine Defense Section Employee

attributes.content: You remind me of my former supervisor at times. I had a lot of respect for her, but she allowed her personal sentiments to destroy her future.
attributes.name: Rhine Defense Section Employee

attributes.content: I don't want to see you repeat her mistakes.
attributes.name: Rhine Defense Section Employee

attributes.content: Ha... sentiments?
attributes.name: Mary

attributes.content: Maybe this could save some people...
attributes.name: Mary

attributes.content: But it can't save one out to get herself killed.
attributes.name: Mary

attributes.content: This is an emergency communication.
attributes.name: Rhine Defense Section Employee

attributes.content: Paging Director Clooney.
attributes.name: Rhine Defense Section Employee

attributes.name: Elena

attributes.content: Base particle structure is stable.

attributes.name: Elena

attributes.content: (I have to get these reports to the boss once we have comms back.)
attributes.name: Elena

attributes.content: ...Elena?
attributes.name: Silence

attributes.content: *cough* *cough*
attributes.name: Elena

attributes.content: What are you doing here?
attributes.name: Silence

attributes.content: I... I just wanted to move a little, catch my breath.
attributes.name: Elena

attributes.content: I understand that you harbor certain feelings towards the Pioneers... but it's better to stick together.
attributes.name: Silence

attributes.content: The last attack was ten minutes ago, not far from here.
attributes.name: Silence

attributes.content: Getting separated would be dangerous, if those things appear again.
attributes.name: Silence

attributes.content: Alright, I'll go back.
attributes.name: Elena

attributes.content: One second.
attributes.name: Silence

attributes.content: Before you do... don't you have anything to say to me?
attributes.name: Silence

attributes.content: I don't know what you're talking about.
attributes.name: Elena

attributes.content: The Pioneers are not in the most stable condition. Angering them will put Joyce in danger.
attributes.name: Silence

attributes.content: I understand why you didn't want to tell the truth in front of them.
attributes.name: Silence

attributes.content: But it's just the two of us here.
attributes.name: Silence

attributes.content: You wanted to ask about the experiments?
attributes.name: Elena

attributes.content: You're not a project member. You'll need to request permission from the company...
attributes.name: Elena

attributes.content: Stop dodging the question.
attributes.name: Silence

attributes.content: I know you're hiding a lot from me.
attributes.name: Silence

attributes.content: I'm not angry. We're friends, and we're colleagues. Rhine Lab has strict rules on confidentiality, and all of us are used to hiding our opinions, rules or no rules.
attributes.name: Silence

attributes.content: Olivia, I'm not...
attributes.name: Elena

attributes.content: You're not doing it on purpose.
attributes.name: Silence

attributes.content: I know. How could I not?
attributes.name: Silence

attributes.content: There aren't many Infected in the company. When you first came and greeted me at lunch... an Energy Section colleague pulled you aside and whispered to you that I was Infected.
attributes.name: Silence

attributes.content: You visited with me anyway.
attributes.name: Silence

attributes.content: I don't care about those stones on your body. Who doesn't have a flaw or two? Not the ones gossiping behind your back, at the very least.
attributes.name: Elena

attributes.content: Even afterwards... I never cared about the stones in my own body!
attributes.name: Elena

attributes.content: That's the Elena Urbica I know.
attributes.name: Silence

attributes.content: You knew something was not right with the experiments here.
attributes.name: Silence

attributes.content: You knew what those silver things were.
attributes.name: Silence

attributes.content: They're endangering our lives, and those of many innocents outside.
attributes.name: Silence

attributes.content: The Elena I know would not let something like this happen.
attributes.name: Silence

attributes.content: What made you keep quiet?
attributes.name: Silence

attributes.content: Did Ferdinand...
attributes.name: Silence

attributes.content: Olivia... this is my job.
attributes.name: Elena

attributes.content: Just like Helen and so many other researchers who work for Rhine Lab... this is where my dreams can come true.
attributes.name: Elena

attributes.content: You said you were once thankful to Director Parvis and Rhine Lab. I...
attributes.name: Elena

attributes.text: This is all you have to show for a month
You have talent. But neither does anyone else in Columbian science.
You have determination, but it has yet to be tested.
The world is waiting for you to change it. Every chance you waste is potentially a massive loss for yourself, and the era you
I chose you from thousands of candidates. You had better not prove me wrong.

attributes.content: Ferdinand is the goal I strive for.
attributes.name: Elena

attributes.content: What did he promise you? Your own project if you help Director Franks complete this experiment? Or...
attributes.name: Silence

attributes.content: Olivia... you're like my sister, treating me like a little kid sitting around waiting for candy.
attributes.name: Elena

attributes.content: I know you have a lot of misconceptions about Director Clooney. Your investigations over the years have caused him a lot of trouble.
attributes.name: Elena

attributes.content: But none of that matters, it's not my place to defend him.
attributes.name: Elena

attributes.content: But he could have refused Rhodes Island's intervention. And yours.
attributes.name: Elena

attributes.content: He wants to change Rhine Lab, change Columbia... and I believe all he needs is a chance.
attributes.name: Elena

attributes.content: You trust Ferdinand that much?
attributes.name: Silence

attributes.content: Did you know that Rhine...
attributes.name: Silence

attributes.content: Who's there?
attributes.name: Silence

attributes.content: Did those things catch up to us?
attributes.name: Elena

attributes.content: It's the Pioneer Team!
attributes.name: Silence

attributes.content: Stay back!
attributes.name: Pioneer Team Member

attributes.content: The captain was right... we're just lab beasts to you...
attributes.name: Pioneer Team Member

attributes.content: You've got it all wrong...
attributes.name: Silence

attributes.content: Still trying to trick us?
attributes.name: Pioneer Team Member

attributes.content: I won't fall for that again! Everything you did for us, it's all fake!
attributes.name: Pioneer Team Member

attributes.content: Calm down, er... Myers, was it?
attributes.name: Silence

attributes.content: Myers, if you won't listen to us, maybe you'll listen to Sonny.
attributes.name: Silence

attributes.content: I don't... I don't want to die here...
attributes.name: Pioneer Team Member

attributes.content: There's no end to this damned corridor... it bears down on you and chokes you out. It's like the walls in the Infected containment zones.
attributes.name: Pioneer Team Member

attributes.content: Let us go... please... I'm begging you...
attributes.name: Pioneer Team Member

attributes.content: I... I'll kill her if you don't!
attributes.name: Pioneer Team Member

attributes.content: Joyce!
attributes.name: Silence

attributes.content: How could this be...?
attributes.name: Elena

attributes.content: No, let Joyce go... don't hurt her!
attributes.name: Elena

attributes.content: The tracks show she passed through here.
attributes.name: Mechanist

attributes.content: Can you tell which way she went?
attributes.name: Saria

attributes.content: The alley up ahead.
attributes.name: Mechanist

attributes.content: Let's go.
attributes.name: Saria

attributes.content: Did you learn anything new, Doctor?
attributes.name: Saria

attributes.content: I'm not concerned about the outcome of a single battle.
attributes.name: Saria

attributes.content: ...I get what the Doctor is saying.
attributes.name: Mechanist

attributes.content: That Liberi isn't strong enough to beat us.
attributes.name: Mechanist

attributes.content: But she's not so weak that she couldn't hold out for a few minutes.
attributes.name: Mechanist

attributes.options: She could have gotten away before Mechanist arrived.
Seems like she was waiting for Mechanist and I to arrive.;Seems like she intended to leave a message behind.

attributes.content: She's luring us into the alley.
attributes.name: Saria

attributes.content: Should we still go?
attributes.name: Mechanist

attributes.content: We're ready.
attributes.name: Columbian Mercenary

attributes.content: On it.
attributes.name: Ho

attributes.content: They'll be coming, right?
attributes.name: Columbian Mercenary

attributes.content: I know Saria. She'll come, even if she knows it's exactly what I want.
attributes.name: Ho

attributes.content: I'm still a little uneasy... that power armor...
attributes.name: Columbian Mercenary

attributes.content: Are you sure we don't need permission from Ferdinand?
attributes.name: Columbian Mercenary

attributes.content: We could always go back to plan A, if you want.
attributes.name: Ho

attributes.content: You mean... never mind, forget that I said anything.
attributes.name: Columbian Mercenary

attributes.content: This is a test.
attributes.name: Ho

attributes.name: Ho

attributes.content: I hear footsteps.
attributes.name: Columbian Mercenary

attributes.name: Columbian Mercenary
